### Create Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/create_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ParentClass": "Actor",
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint"
}

### Create Function
POST http://localhost:8080/create_function
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "FunctionName": "MyFunction",
  "FunctionInputSignature": "int32 Input1, float Input2 ",
  "FunctionOutputSignature": "bool Output"
}

### Edit Function
POST http://localhost:8080/edit_function
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "FunctionName": "MyFunction",
  "FunctionInputSignature": "int32 NewInput,float Input2,FString ExtraInput",
  "FunctionOutputSignature": "bool NewOutput,float ExtraOutput"
}

### Delete Function
POST http://localhost:8080/delete_function
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "FunctionName": "MyFunction"
}

### Add Node to Graph (unified) — Function call via ClassName::FunctionName
POST http://localhost:8080/add_node_to_graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeTypeName": "/Script/Engine.Actor::K2_GetActorLocation"
}

### Add Node — Function call (same BP) via node_type_name + function_name
POST http://localhost:8080/add_node_to_graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeTypeName": "CallFunction",
  "FunctionName": "MyFunction"
}

### Add Node — Custom Event
POST http://localhost:8080/add_node_to_graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeTypeName": "CustomEvent",
  "EventName": "MyEvent",
  "bIsCustomEvent": true,
  "EventSignature": "int32 Param1, float Param2"
}

### Add Node — Built-in Event
POST http://localhost:8080/add_node_to_graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeTypeName": "Event",
  "EventName": "ReceiveHit",
  "bIsCustomEvent": false
}

### Add Node — Variable setter
POST http://localhost:8080/add_node_to_graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeTypeName": "VariableSet",
  "VarName": "Test",
  "bIsSetter": true
}

### Add Node — Variable getter
POST http://localhost:8080/add_node_to_graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeTypeName": "VariableGet",
  "VarName": "DefaultSceneRoot",
  "bIsSetter": false
}

### Get Blueprint Variables
GET http://localhost:8080/get_blueprint_variables?bp_path=/Game/Test/MyBlueprint

### Get Blueprint Functions
GET http://localhost:8080/get_blueprint_functions?bp_path=/Game/Test/MyBlueprint

### Get Graph
GET http://localhost:8080/get_graph?bp_path=/Game/Test/MyBlueprint&graph_name=EventGraph


### Compile Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/compile_blueprint?bp_path=/Game/Test/MyBlueprint

### Get Supported Nodes (call before add_node_to_graph to see valid node_type_name / ClassName::FunctionName)
GET http://localhost:8080/get_supported_nodes

### Add Variable to Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/add_variable_to_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "VarSignature": "float NewVar99"
}

### Delete Variable from Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/delete_variable_from_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "VarName": "NewVar4"
}

### Rename Variable in Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/rename_variable_in_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "OldVarName": "NewVar2",
  "NewVarName": "RenamedVar"
}

### Set Variable Default Value in Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/set_variable_default_value_in_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "VarName": "NewVar",
  "DefaultValue": "3.14159"
}

### Connect Pins in Graph
POST http://localhost:8080/connect_pins
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "OutputNodeId": "7C40B46046D4D873D5DF9C89D957426E",
  "OutputPinName": "NewVar5",
  "InputNodeId": "2AFEFE7B4F381FCD206A47903659176F",
  "InputPinName": "TargetRelativeLocation"
}

### Break Connection between Pins in Graph
POST http://localhost:8080/break_pin_connection
Content-Type: application/json

{
"BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
"GraphName": "EventGraph",
"OutputNodeId": "7C40B46046D4D873D5DF9C89D957426E",
"OutputPinName": "NewVar5",
"InputNodeId": "2AFEFE7B4F381FCD206A47903659176F",
"InputPinName": "TargetRelativeLocation"
}

### Set Pin Default Value in Graph
POST http://localhost:8080/set_pin_default_value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "GraphName": "EventGraph",
  "NodeId": "2AFEFE7B4F381FCD206A47903659176F",
  "PinName": "TargetRelativeLocation",
  "DefaultValue": "100, 200, 300"
}

