### Get Components of Blueprint
GET http://localhost:8080/get_components_of_bp?bp_path=/Game/Test/MyBlueprint3

### Add Component to Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/add_component_to_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "ComponentClass": "StaticMeshComponent",
  "ComponentName": "MyStaticMeshComp",
  "AttachTo": "DefaultSceneRoot"
}

### Rename Component in Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/rename_component_in_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "ComponentName": "MyStaticMeshComp2",
  "NewComponentName": "RenamedComp"
}

### Delete Component from Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/remove_component_from_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "ComponentName": "RenamedComp"
}

### Reparent Component in Blueprint
POST http://localhost:8080/reattach_component_in_bp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "ComponentName": "MyStaticMeshComp2",
  "AttachTo": "MyStaticMeshComp"
}

### Get Component Properties
GET http://localhost:8080/get_component_properties?bp_path=/Game/Test/MyBlueprint&component_name=MyStaticMeshComp

### Set Component Property
POST http://localhost:8080/set_component_property
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "BpPath": "/Game/Test/MyBlueprint",
  "ComponentName": "MyStaticMeshComp",
  "Properties": {
    "RelativeLocation": "X=0.5,Y=20,Z=100",
    "StaticMesh": "/Engine/BasicShapes/Cube.Cube",
    "Mobility": "Movable"
  }
}